      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: clear timeout timer in Tailscale binary probe Promise.race",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes an issue where `findTailscaleBinary` would leave a dangling timer after each binary check because `Promise.race` with a `setTimeout` was never cleared when `runExec` completed first.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\nWrap the `Promise.race` in `try/finally` that captures and clears the timer handle.\n\n## User Impact\n\nNo user-visible change. Prevents a minor resource leak during Tailscale binary discovery.\n\n## Evidence\n\n```\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\n     Tests  30 passed (30)\nDuration  1.83s\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 12.30s\n```\n\nSame cleanup pattern already used in `src/node-host/with-timeout.ts:37-45`.",
